bpp_1.0.3
---------------------------------
- Corrected color error in basicPlot() for futility boundary.
- Added wrapper functions for easier use for binary, continuous, and time-to-event endpoint.
  These functions are bpp_binary, bpp_continuous, bpp_t2e, bpp_1interim_binary, bpp_1interim_continuous, bpp_1interim_t2e.
- Renamed datasigma --> interimSE, finalsigma --> finalSE.

